quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,60,"E …ďen …ďe no tinnoo e golle dewal ngal, …ďe …ďattora ka Alla golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen hara hi…ďe huli fii wata Alla ronku ja…ďannde …ďe nafkugol ma…ď…ďe ngol e golle ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īe …óen si …ďe ruttoyike ka Makko √Ďalnde Darngal."
  23,61,"∆Āen sifaa…ďe …óii sifaaji maw…ói, hi…ďe he√Īoo faade e golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe adondiray…ďe e majje, ko sabu …óum …ďe adori tanaa ma…ď…ďe."
  23,62,"Men fawaali wonkii woo si wanaa emmbere ko ki hattanaa kon gollugol, Deftere no ka Amen Men tabintinii e nder mayre gollal kala gollu…óo, hinde wowla Goonga, kan ka sikke woo alah e nder mu'un, hara kam…ďe …ďe too√Īiroytaake uytaneede mo∆ī∆īi ma…ď…ďe …óin, wanaa fii non …ďeydaneede bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin."
  23,63,"Ko woni, …ďer…óe heefer…ďe …ďen no e nder welsindaa- re immorde ndee Deftere, nden wowlaynde Goo- nga kan, e Deftere jippiinde nden e ma…ď…ďe, no woodani …ďe kadi golle goo gaanin …óe …ďe woni …óen e mu'un immorde e keefeeru ko kam…ďe gollata …óe."
  23,64,"Haa si Men leptirii neeminaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ka ngurdan aduna Lepte …óen √Ďalnde Darngal tawa kam…ďe hi…ďe towna hitooji ma…ď…ďe …óin ko …ďe faabnatoo…ďe."
  23,65,"Wi'anee …ďe ka ta∆īinngol …ďe e Yurmeende Alla nden: "Wata on haacu wata on …óa…ď…ďu faabo e ndee √Ďalaande, ko pellet, on marah walloowo mo no ha…óana on immorde e Lepte Alla …óen"."
  23,66,"Gom…óii laatinoke Aayeeje Deftere Alla nden no janngetenoo e dow moo…óon ka aduna, laati…óon hi…óon ruttoo ko on huccu…ďe(runtii) e gaayi majje, si on nanii …óe sabu a√Īugol …óe."
  23,67,"Hi…óon wa…óa …óum ko on mawnintinii…ďe e dow yim…ďe …ďen sabu ko aa∆īi…óon kon wonndema onon ko on yim…ďe hurum on hara le on laataaki yim…ďe makko; sabu yim…ďe [hurum on] ko kam…ďe woni huloo…ďe Alla …ďen, hi…óon hiirira …ďannge [hurum on] ko boni kon immorde e konngol ngol, hara onon on la…ď…ďinaali mo."
  23,68,"Kaa hara …ďee sirkoo…ďe taskaaki ko Alla jippini kon ka Alqur'aana fii yo …ďe gom…óin nde, …ďe gollira ko woni kon e nder mayre, kaa aru e ma…ď…ďe ko araali maamiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ado ma…ď…ďe? ∆Āe …óurnii nde …ďe fenni nde."
  23,69,"Kaa hara kam…ďe …ďe andaali Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) on mo Alla Nuli faade e ma…ď…ďe, hara kam…ďe ko …ďe faytu…ďe mo? Gom…óii …ďe anndiino mo, …ďe anndiino kadi Goongugol makko e hoolaare makko nden."
  23,70,"Ko woni, hi…ďe wi'a: "Kanko ko o feetu…óo, gom…óii …ďe fenniino, ko woni, o addanii …ďe Goonga kan, kan ka sikke woo alaa e muu…óum wonndema ko ka immorde ka Alla, heewu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe ko a√Īu…ďe Goonga kan, ko …ďe a√Īu…ďe ka sabu a√Īude mbo e haasidaagu wonngu ka wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe, ej inngan- gol meere ma…ď…ďe nden."
  23,71,"Sinndo Alla na…ďirno fiyakuuji …óin, O fewjiri …ói wano wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin weliraa non kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin bonayno, e …ďen wonu…ďe e majji sabu majjugol ma…ď…ďe battane fiyakuuji …óin, ko selli kon e ko boni kon immorde e fewjugol ngol."
  23,72,"Kaa a …óa…ď…ďu -an Nulaa…óo- njo…ďdi immorde e …ďee e dow ko addan…óaa …ďe kon, hara ko …óum wa…ói haa …ďe salii noddaandu ndun? ∆äum iwraali e maa…óa, ko mbarjaari Joomi maa…óa ndin e njo…ďdi Makko ndin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude diini mbarjaari …ďee e tanaa ma…ď…ďe, ko Kanko -Senii…óo On- woni Mo∆ī∆īo Arsikoowo."
  23,73,"Pellet an Nulaa…óo on, hi…óa noddude …ďee e tanaa ma…ď…ďe faade e laawol focciingol, ngol oo√Īannde alah e muu…óum, ngol ko Laawol Lislaamu ngol."
  23,74,"E pellet, …ďen …ďe gom…óinaali Laakara on e ko woni ton kon immorde e hasboore e Lepte e mbarjaari, ko …ďe oo√Īii…ďe e Laawol Lislaamu ngol …ďe jokki tanaa maggol immorde e laawi …ďoylii…ói yottinay…ói faade e Yiite ngen."